Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

python-sstimap (Automatic SSTI detection and interactive tool)

SSTImap is a penetration testing software that can check websites
for Code Injection and Server-Side Template Injection vulnerabilities
and exploit them, giving access to the operating system itself.

HOME: https://github.com/vladko312/SSTImap

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-mechanize 

